Class BlockPdu

java.lang.Object
  uk.co.westhawk.snmp.pdu.BlockPdu
public class BlockPdu
extends java.lang.Object

The BlockPdu class is a wrapper class that will block until it receives the answer.

public void setBulkParameters(int nr,
